    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This 2008 Porsche 911 Carrera features the revered 3.6L M97 horizontally opposed flat-six, delivering a linear power band and an unmistakable acoustic signature. Mated to a precise 6-speed manual transaxle, the drivetrain offers exceptional mechanical engagement. The chassis remains taut, utilizing its multi-link rear suspension and McPherson struts to provide the communicative steering feedback synonymous with the 997 platform. This example has been fastidiously maintained, showing consistent oil pressure and smooth synchronization across all gears. Recent preventative maintenance includes a fresh drive belt and a comprehensive inspection of the cooling system. A mechanically sound, driver-focused specimen ready for spirited canyon carving.",
      "price": 36500.0,
