      "description": "This vehicle represents a well-maintained example that balances performance with daily utility. The exterior paint retains a high-gloss finish, showing only minor, age-appropriate peppering on the front fascia from highway driving. The body is straight with no significant dings or scratches. Inside, the cabin is smoke-free and features supple leather seating with minimal bolster wear; all electronic components, including the navigation system and heated seats, function as intended. Mechanically, the car is sound, having recently undergone a full multi-point inspection. We have just replaced the brake pads and performed a synthetic oil service. The tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, and the transmission shifts smoothly through all gears. Included are two sets of keys and a comprehensive folder of service receipts. This is an honest, reliable car ready for its next owner.",
